{"tid":55262,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"【健身】講下二頭肌(老鼠仔)新手玩法","createTime":"2016-12-26T09:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T07:12:35.000Z","uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"caef2d97bfd3ee2c97987c1dbcf85f7680258d78","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"肱二頭肌 , 即係二頭肌 , 俗稱老鼠仔或手瓜<br />\n<br />\n二頭肌係由兩條肌肉所組成 , 一條長頭一條短頭 , 所以叫二頭肌 , 一般黎講二頭肌的長頭同短頭並不能獨立發力 , 所以有些人說長頭同短頭並無方法或無須分開練<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gymbeginner.hk/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/arm-science-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gymbeginner.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2Farm-science-2.jpg&h=67454265&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然說長短頭不能獨立練 , 但其實都可以用針對性嘅動作去練 , 因為一般動作好少會真正用到長頭 , 所以你可能會發現不斷做彎舉都做不大二頭 , 原因係大部分彎舉動作只針對二頭的短頭 , 前面講過長短頭係無法分開 , 當你彎舉的動作係 7成練短頭 , 3 成練長頭時 , 短頭明明仲未攰 , 但長頭做幾下已經開始無力 , 咁樣就變左由短頭獨力支撐9成甚至10成重量 , 咁情況練力還可以 , 如果想練大就會因為次數太少刺激不足而練不大了 ...<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n最常見練二頭方式<br />\n<br />\n斜板 / 牧師椅<br />\n前斜板 , 大概有70%練短頭 , 30%練長頭<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gymbeginner.hk/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Partial.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gymbeginner.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2FPartial.png&h=31b6f9bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直立彎舉<br />\n大概有55%練短頭 , 45%練長頭 , 缺點係容易借左腰力同膊頭力 , 事倍功半<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gymbeginner.hk/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/bb-curl-e1400075706363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gymbeginner.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F05%2Fbb-curl-e1400075706363.jpg&h=951a8626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直立鎚手彎舉<br />\n大概有40%練短頭 , 60%練長頭 , 缺點都係容易借左腰力同膊頭力<br />\n<img src=\"https://9298-presscdn-0-7-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/One-Arm-Standing-Dumbbell-Hammer-Curl-neutral-grip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F9298-presscdn-0-7-pagely.netdna-ssl.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2FOne-Arm-Standing-Dumbbell-Hammer-Curl-neutral-grip.jpg&h=505516cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仰後斜板彎舉<br />\n大概有30%練短頭 , 70%練長頭 , 睇落好似唔難 , 不過新手玩住 5磅先啦 , 無錯係唔5磅 , 唔洗怕醜 , 做得完 10 x 4sets 先 #lol# <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gymbeginner.hk/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/incline-offset-thumb-dumbbell-curl_470x360_11-e1415619878171.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gymbeginner.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F05%2Fincline-offset-thumb-dumbbell-curl_470x360_11-e1415619878171.jpg&h=8c0c0d23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d4b7f46f6ddb51b470485b133ea436872d38f82","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"錯誤的「仰後斜板彎舉」,手臂用膊借力屈左上去了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://9298-presscdn-0-7-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/incline-bench-dumbbell-bicep-curl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F9298-presscdn-0-7-pagely.netdna-ssl.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2Fincline-bench-dumbbell-bicep-curl.jpg&h=e593d251&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ce3c81a541bd5fc33ffb0baaf560c3e62d43bc2","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fbbf94c565e44598c8af607e811cd9bba20a55","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f331ad6f478b2f3e6719d28b96637f539328a186","tid":55262,"uid":7719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:08:46.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f1621afdb300b07f9625838568e5294a51a943d4","tid":55262,"uid":49730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"084bfae187859861b3123db17d7064ab23b31bf7","tid":55262,"uid":29143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad804e00c6f6c06e296f39593dd04aadb5e2f881","tid":55262,"uid":29143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:20:30.000Z","msg":"我想操厚啲個身 巴打有咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71aa64e7bf4f3aa11632d58154a4afd1788d7bde","tid":55262,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:21:55.000Z","msg":"2頭肌真係無咩難度<br />\n講下3頭肌重好"},{"pid":"dc6b3a1e90df0507b1f01b5bd23b6efb35fec9bb","tid":55262,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2頭肌真係無咩難度<br />\n講下3頭肌重好</blockquote><br />\n3頭都無咩難度<br />\n要講就講後博"},{"pid":"d7623de750154a766df5c1837a81200cd2fec0e0","tid":55262,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2頭肌真係無咩難度<br />\n講下3頭肌重好</blockquote><br />\n二三頭都唔難啦"},{"pid":"8d8ce524f6be91b8126d1126c9cedd73e7ccc579","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2頭肌真係無咩難度<br />\n講下3頭肌重好</blockquote><br />\n二三頭都唔難啦</blockquote><br />\n新手期三頭係易過二頭 , 做掌上壓已經練到三頭初型"},{"pid":"3b7edd238da93cc1537ad8f3a47ed272a93323b1","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想操厚啲個身 巴打有咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n練胸背走唔甩啦 , 我果度有個人只練胸唔練背 , 個上身成個鑊咁 , 寒背唔似寒背 , 好似企唔直咁"},{"pid":"6109e601745bd042ad644bf6472000f0a4d99848","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"開錯台，明明想開喺潮流台"},{"pid":"cc10f437938c38bb1f45b7d7582f0a3d9b4e50bf","tid":55262,"uid":38571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:02:08.000Z","msg":"吾係我留名學野"},{"pid":"fbe0fd3c5968338c896f136c4598c7932272c1dd","tid":55262,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"玩具台 笑左"},{"pid":"ec2c21478688123848b98a10d1ac6847397e1ca3","tid":55262,"uid":32615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:54:09.000Z","msg":"玩具台<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f82f60eedef6d883a14c5e579df3f5fedfec98","tid":55262,"uid":65736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e0caf194bd1f5c498837e987016214611f196893","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc17f0f1a618b3db7cacb4f7be4d61ac5e80f0a","tid":55262,"uid":38976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d6297293e6c23a0e93af5891872d456b343d4fca","tid":55262,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:47:04.000Z","msg":"第一個post 最後果個動作真係好難用力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舉十磅已經冇晒力咁"},{"pid":"dc4640086248a42561f2d6fbbf3b4d016da12e3b","tid":55262,"uid":59882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名"},{"pid":"e710c04b124e5f7d105cd2a934012585012fa2ac","tid":55262,"uid":67279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:09:08.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7f0ec4fbdd3c1183526fb3aa5dff1d291a03a328","tid":55262,"uid":31146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我恢復得好慢咁 但我已經一日訓7個鐘左右 今日推佐幾下胸 已經無曬力"},{"pid":"872bc2f7d97288f6d77844a2865fc10b89737303","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解我恢復得好慢咁 但我已經一日訓7個鐘左右 今日推佐幾下胸 已經無曬力</blockquote><br />\n舉前果兩餐飯食得唔飽 ?"},{"pid":"21b2bb78919d9e5999679e22c170739a731eda7e","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一個post 最後果個動作真係好難用力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舉十磅已經冇晒力咁</blockquote><br />\n所以咪話玩5 磅 4x10 先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14615a7817cd5906835ee3dd6f325a61b91104a2","tid":55262,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解我恢復得好慢咁 但我已經一日訓7個鐘左右 今日推佐幾下胸 已經無曬力</blockquote><br />\n大肌肉eg胸背腿，最好休兩三日再玩，回得比較好，如果唔係就代表食唔夠或強度太強，肌肉未適應"},{"pid":"d7f3025df27d9f557259186de81ffa5a80bbb390","tid":55262,"uid":62079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2頭肌真係無咩難度<br />\n講下3頭肌重好</blockquote><br />\n二三頭都唔難啦</blockquote><br />\n新手期三頭係易過二頭 , 做掌上壓已經練到三頭初型</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心想學三頭同背"},{"pid":"8dac91607217eb433060dc252cf66deea7d1696d","tid":55262,"uid":38755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"408935a33aa7e8849c70f5094f3ecf3d29137b7d","tid":55262,"uid":18304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T06:14:52.000Z","msg":"專門討論健身 歡迎新手高手加入  <br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAD_jxf-uZT35HOry5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAD_jxf-uZT35HOry5w&d=8QKeduE8D59wrLrvr8TMknvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=4786a5f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAD_jxf-uZT35HOry5w</a><br />\n[/url]直接入link就join到"},{"pid":"ff666a8ee80d3036facccd9ecc300788584c305e","tid":55262,"uid":61888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:45:14.000Z","msg":"二頭好易操,反而肩膀操極都大唔到幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dab812e9a0b4d499fe6341c18a470f419119240","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二頭好易操,反而肩膀操極都大唔到幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細肌肉本身力量唔大 , 所以好容易會借左力 , 例如飛膊 , 係好容易借左斜肌同背肌 , 你 chok 得起 20磅 , 隨時有 15磅係斜肌同背肌嘅力量 , 所以練膊唔係講求重量 , 而係講求持續嘅集中壓力 , 即係用一個比較輕嘅重量 , 琅在 workout 過程中令三角肌幾乎 100% 時間都處於壓力當中 , 亦因為重量輕 , 肌肉比較易控制下斜肌同背肌係可以有意識地不參與<br />\n<br />\n睇一睇張繼聰飛膊相信就明我想講乜 !<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R-1LMdyo1tY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR-1LMdyo1tY&d=8QKeduE8D59wrLrvr8TMknvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=e5c22d44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R-1LMdyo1tY</a>"},{"pid":"d1ea78531d2e36f8e58eca334fe04633d41c7128","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T07:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2頭肌真係無咩難度<br />\n講下3頭肌重好</blockquote><br />\n二三頭都唔難啦</blockquote><br />\n新手期三頭係易過二頭 , 做掌上壓已經練到三頭初型</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心想學三頭同背</blockquote><br />\n練三頭多數都係呢4 個揀3 個做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianshen8.com/uploads/allimg/130719/2_130719153507_4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianshen8.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130719%2F2_130719153507_4.gif&h=ed0d5f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianshen8.com/uploads/allimg/130722/2_130722110336_6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianshen8.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130722%2F2_130722110336_6.gif&h=70a3abc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianshen8.com/uploads/allimg/130722/2_130722112240_8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianshen8.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130722%2F2_130722112240_8.gif&h=baf52517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianshen8.com/uploads/allimg/130722/2_130722111500_3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianshen8.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130722%2F2_130722111500_3.gif&h=9e14cf82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a28f889864796ddee137558d4081dd0652841245","tid":55262,"uid":79673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"有冇啲咩健身timetable share 下 倒如邊日練d 乜 幾多下幾多set 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254aaf5983769b4631cc6d7b10272a8a6c020845","tid":55262,"uid":64889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"0c974833ccba5383943ca70f6132f22c8f19ee39","tid":55262,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇啲咩健身timetable share 下 倒如邊日練d 乜 幾多下幾多set 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"